- ## Interdependencies
#Interdependencies #between #NFRs #Challenges #NonFunctional #Requirements #Software #Engineering 
A major problem is to deal with what they call dynamic interdependencies, i.e., quality characteristics or non-functional requirements, which influ- ence a larger part of the functionality or other characteris- tics of the system. The problem is not only to know that the interdependency exists but also to figure out how the requirements affect each other and how this can be dealt with.
